Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:09.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:22.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Roasted Sweet Potatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's February already...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have yet to even see \NHayate once this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my greatest opportunity \Nof the year is coming up soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! For a young lady, the big event in February is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! Mister, how could \Nyou in front of a young lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good fortune, stay within!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why are you doing this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, what are you saying, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. When it comes \Nto the big event in February,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there could be nothing else but \Nthe bean-throwing exorcism ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't really care, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, it's late, so get ready for bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then to wrap things up, we'll eat \Nas many beans as we are old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maria, you want some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I suppose. \NIt's for good luck, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? All three of you are staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you thinking, "Huh? \NAren't there too few beans here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who looks at you, \Nyou're a young and fresh 17-year-old!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you all covered in sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of you, hurry up and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:04.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, ladies and gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:11.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That a humongous mansion like \Nthis exists somewhere in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:14.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss's name is Nagi Sanzenin. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Her butler's name is Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both a bit clueless
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and both have a bit of the \Nwrong idea about each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:27.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but they share the immensely strong, \Nloving bond between servant and mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my back... Owowowow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\N I don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:38.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai! \NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:44.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\N The future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:49.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honne o misecha make datoka \NStuff like, showing your true feelings means defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:54.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentaku hajiku jinsei datoka\N Or a life tapping away at a calculator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:59.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro o itsuwaru kurai nara\N Rather than be false to myself like that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:05.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichiten-battou baka-shoujiki mo kuuzen-zetsugo! \NI'll struggle to be uniquely naïve and honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:10.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Komatta kao o mireba ki-ni-naru shi\N If I see a troubled look, I'll be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:15.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinsei isogu riyuu mo betsuni nai shi \NAnd it's not like I've got a reason to hurry through life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:21.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu wa kimi ni azukeyou \NI'll entrust you with the treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:27.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin yori-michi datte tsukiau yo! \NI'll even keep you company on your free-ranging detours
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkii-sugiru tenkai \NA development that's way too lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae wa mayowanai \NI won't hesitate to give my answer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:38.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kantan sa! Subete wa kimi no tame ni \NIt's easy! It's all for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuhyou wa ki-ni-shinai \NI won't worry about the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:44.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rettou-kan ni doujinai!\N I won't let a sense of inferiority get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:49.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakedasu shunkan wa ima koko ni aru \NThe moment to start running is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Maria Appreciation Day! In February
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.31,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Video Rental V Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. We ended up \Noffending Maria again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make too much trouble for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not going to be \Nyoung forever, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something so terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not say such a terrible thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Maria works non-stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind \Nof expert she is as a maid,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a fact that she must \Nhave a lot of built up fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is always being so good to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if we could \Nshow her our appreciation somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is where \NI'll become a maid and...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you do that, it will be \Neven more exhausting for Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not the sort to take a break \Njust because you tell her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have just the right plan for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:58.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Approximately an hour later...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world \Nare we going all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder where.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to wait to get there to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to be staying here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki actually gave us a great idea, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies' Stay Plan, Relaxation Tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends went there the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay at a luxurious midtown hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go to the spa and get beauty treatments...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just sit back and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like rewarding yourself \Nfor your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it's popular among \Nworking young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...young women...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young... Young... Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is it! Make the \Narrangements right away, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we call it "Thank you \Nfor everything, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The big sister appreciation \Nrelaxation plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! B-But... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a present from the Miss \Nto show you her appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for what you do every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for always working \Nso hard for us, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for today and tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forget about your work and enjoy \Na day off in the city at your leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will take you up on your offer \Nand take a nice long break...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Work off that fatigue \Nto your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined Hayata and \Nhis gang would be coming to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall take that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Maria and I will \Ntake the room over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I shall start \Nby getting the tea ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are on break, so please take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, y-yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate has made all kinds \Nof arrangements for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:05.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? This is the Imperial Suite. \NWe would like some room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pool, the jacuzzi, the gym, \Nplus the nail and beauty salons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, a pot of royal milk tea, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have free access to all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this hotel's selling point \Nis their service towards young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly perfect for you, \Na working {\i1}young{\i0} woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't emphasize the \N"young" part so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me. Room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? \NDon't I look cool? Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Committee Chairman! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a one-day hands-on \Ninternship through our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about this on the news before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, today was specially \Ndiscounted by 5 for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I settled on this place, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:58.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Today, this hotel is riddled \Nwith people from Hakuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Hayate and his gang just earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn. I was hoping we might \Nget to see Yoshizumi or Orlando.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshizumi? Because the Tokyo Metropolitan \NGovernment building is right in front of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind. Anyway, where's Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got caught by the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think back, \Nit was during the Tokyo Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I got into this line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:22.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get what he's saying at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here so Maria \Ncould have a relaxing time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me. My thrifty habits \Ngot the better of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's already happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, I'll do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you guys doing here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! I'm so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll help you! \NI'll ask everyone to help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:53.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Segawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have a tremendously...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if it's about me, \Nplease don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am already relaxing more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We cannot lose heart now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect Maria's \Nday off, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you and Maria will go \Non to Stage 2 of the Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will meet again here in 3 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, um, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is starting \Nto look a bit like a battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It was true. In a certain sense, \Nit was a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going, Maria? \NAre you working off that fatigue good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My! How fabulous! \NIt's like a rose petal bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but this is the pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I don't recall \Nasking for such a service.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks needed. In exchange, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.28,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill to: Sanzenin Nagi \NRoses
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Himuro, is that enough now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was satisfactory. Did you \Nlearn something, Little Master Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's tough to have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, as for Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man... The people of Hakuou \Nare already here, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that rate, it w‎ill be \Nutterly impossible for you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand is my foot... My foot is my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to satisfactorily entertain the guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pull ourselves together \Nand go for beauty treatments next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best to get that fatigue \Nworked off for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I will, but Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:37.36,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Special Marvelous Anti-Aging Course
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About this "Super Special \NMarvelous Anti-Aging Course"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the details! I'll be next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gack! Y-You're that piece-of-junk robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're actually pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course, because I'm always \Ndoing massages for Miss Makimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, I guess I'll do my best \Nto work off my fatigue, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about what's going \Non from Miss Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a nice opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought I'd learn \Na trade, so I'll be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I ever get fired from my teaching job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use all my powers to totally \Nwork off that fatigue of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I sense a rather serious error...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I sense danger here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there goes my fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:42.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there goes my fatigue! \NMy fatigue's totally going away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be awfully weary, Miss Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, somehow, I'm already 28 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay that I'm still up \Nto the same old silliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder sometimes, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are still you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you agonize over it, \Nyou'll never be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be true to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, please do be careful \Nnot to drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See how your liver acupoint is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've met a great senpai of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But um, I'm over 10 years \Nyounger than you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maria, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a whiff of something ominous...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no, it's nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a sense that \Nsomething sinister is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your new outfit suits you \Nvery well, Mistress Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, I special ordered it from COSPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that in the end, I ought to \Nalways be dressed up in formal attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look fabulous, Mistress Kuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Sion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I inspect this place, I am going \Nto raise my blood sugar level a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mistress Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued, in an ever less \Nsoothing and relaxing direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laid back and relaxed.\N({\u1}No{\u0}nbiri yutta{\u1}ri{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rhythmically start the word game!\N({\u1}Ri{\u0}zumu de shiritori sutaato!)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tan-tan, nta-nta, pase{\u1}ru{\u0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:23.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they are both enjoying \Ntheir relaxed day off in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate, I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. Wait, um, where's Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going for a stroll around the garden \Nor something and taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking it easy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! She's taking it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:48.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If Maria isn't going to be coming \Nback to the room for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate and I will be alone together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make us some tea now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:57.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And we're in a suite, like the kind \Na newly-wed couple might stay in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even taking a break \Nis not easily accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those two have shown \Nsuch concern for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're here, I should do \Nas they wish and take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um, I would like to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that this is where \NHakuou's internship is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are in Episode 45
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and for the first time \NI have reached my destination!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid that I would never \Nreach it for the rest of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I felt such uncertainty \Nand anxiety and confusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us start by going to \Nthe front desk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never expected that you would \Nparticipate in an event like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would use this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to learn a little about the ways of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ladies of Hakuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not seem to have been \Nfocusing for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's because it's a bit too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's turn the TV on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Mr. Sanma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! This will put Hayate in the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:24.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, but it's too soon \Nfor us! It's too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I actually like \Nthis actress quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gained a noticeable glow about her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since she split with that kabuki actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is Maria doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,How much freedom must she enjoy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She's actually not taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Make sure to also tuck in \Nthe top sheet properly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then line up the bedcover neatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the key to making it look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I accidentally double-booked a room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? I am so very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would like a twin bed instead \Nof a double, we could arrange that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here and started working
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the year of the Japan \NWorld Exposition. Back in 1971.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japan World Exposition was in 1970.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, total attendance \Nwas 64,218,770.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,77 countries participated, including Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as 4 international organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're on break, aren't you? \NShouldn't you be taking it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not tell Nagi \Nand Hayate about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! There's trouble! Big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Maripon, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maripon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Miss Makimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could it be that \Nyou two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want you \Nto help me with, Mariachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mariachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, the cafeteria is just \Nall "high school" and it's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, please don't hold back the 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I dunno what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two of us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mari...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Don't let her know I'm calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Maria wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was cleaning when I found \Nsomething a guest had left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the room number?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll look up the guest's \Ncontact information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where's the concierge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was over there just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ni hao. Wo jiao Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell Nagi about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you need me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind doing something for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the next sweet ready yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our patissier was creating sweets \Nat a furious pace to keep up with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he has collapsed \Ndue to utter exhaustion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How feeble of him! \NI have still not had enough to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our special mont blanc \Nfrom our secret menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rich, yet refreshing sweetness, \Nwhich envelops the tongue like velvet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it is delicious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am canceling my inspection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to return to the academy \Nbefore this aftertaste vanishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wow, Maria's recipe worked like a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, because it's been \Nproven effective before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Ignore what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Miss Makimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing? I'm just \Nreading a book and eating cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean, what about providing guidance \Nfor the interns or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey! You're appalled, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake is important for the brain, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please show him \Nto the washroom immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! I knew it had to be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cake tasted the same as what \NI once had during the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while since I have been \Nfully satisfied. You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you see fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I think it's about time \NI got back to Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened after that \Nand the day ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired. I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, want to eat something on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any money, \Nright? We'll treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any pride as an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Because \NI'm gonna be true to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual for her \Nto fall asleep at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the unfamiliar \Nsurroundings wore her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss was really geared up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was determined that you \Nwere going to have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Maria. So your \Nexhaustion's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. I'm grateful \Nfor everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being at the residence really is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the appreciation tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much to both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seeing the bright smiles on your faces
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the faces of everyone \Nhere at the residence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the best gift there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that is wonderful to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to continuing \Nto work with you, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, your skin \Nis shiny smooth, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that Super Special Marvelous \NAnti-Aging Course worked, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You practically look like a young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly look rejuvenated, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So 17 is no longer a young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or am I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no! No, you're not, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:51.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, next time, they'll battle \Nthe brilliant sweat of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:06.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaretai fureraretetai\NI want to be loved, to feel that touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Motomeru bakari no kimochi wa\NThe sense of continually seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:15.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibi o kumoraseteta\NUsed to darken my days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:23.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ni deau sono hi made wa\NUntil the day I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde sora ni hibiku-youni\NCall my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:42.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi-michi mo kitto futari nara\NEven lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:48.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunaida te to te hanasanai\NI won't let go of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:51.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoritainda\NI want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:57.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saa ikou bokura wa\NCome on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:09.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima o mitsumete aruki-hajimeru\N...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.05,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council Girl Trio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.05,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Lettering by Eri Nakao
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The student council girl \Ntrio's Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:29.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there, friends, I'm Izumi Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Risa Asakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the warrior of freedom, Miki Hanabishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you watching TV
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are naturally certain to have \Nmemorized our image song already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, because they should be listening \Nto it at least 100 times a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have happy news for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you collect 10 belly bands \Nfrom our CDs and send it in...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't win anything in particular!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.94,0:23:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, here's today's fan service \Nshot you've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, this one's pervy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, talk about daring, \Nfirst thing in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.32,0:23:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:24:00.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on here?! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:19.31,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:02.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You ask the most nonsense \Nquestions sometimes, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:03.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:06.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi put on a blazer and got \Non a bus with no hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's fallen \Nfor a guy at another school,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:10.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's sneaking in \Nby wearing their uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:11.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.46,0:24:13.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "His Name Is \NMagic Ball Pitcher Wataru!!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Young Sir won't come to me \Nfor advice, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:17.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's probably \Nbecause it's easier for him
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:19.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,to talk to Miss Nagi, who is his age,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:20.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,or some other equally trivial reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Name Is Magic \NBall Pitcher Wataru!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:25.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Cross Triangle with "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" again next time!
